<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Ajukan Antrian — Perpustakaan SMA PESAT</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="app-layout">
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <main class="main-content">
    <!-- Topbar -->
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="topbar-search">
        <span class="topbar-search-icon">
          <svg width="16" height="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <form action="/api/peminjam/searchBook" method="GET" style="display:contents;">
          <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Cari Koleksi...">
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Page Body -->
    <div class="page-body">
      <div style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <!-- Back -->
        <div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          <a href="/api/peminjam/katalog" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">
            <svg width="14" height="14" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9.707 16.707a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-6-6a1 1 0 010-1.414l6-6a1 1 0 011.414 1.414L5.414 9H17a1 1 0 110 2H5.414l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 010 1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Kembali ke Katalog
          </a>
        </div>

        <h1 class="page-title">Ajukan Antrian</h1>

        <!-- Info Box -->
        <div class="alert alert-info" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
          Stok buku sedang habis. Kamu bisa mendaftar antrian dan akan diberitahu ketika buku tersedia.
        </div>

        <!-- Confirm Card -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body" style="text-align:center;padding:40px 28px;">
            <div style="font-size:56px;margin-bottom:16px;">⏳</div>
            <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px;">Daftarkan Diri ke Antrian?</h2>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-sm);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:28px;">
              Anda akan mendapatkan nomor antrian. Kami akan memberi tahu Anda ketika buku tersedia untuk dipinjam.
            </p>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <a href="/api/peminjam/katalog" class="btn btn-secondary">Batal</a>
              <form action="/api/peminjam/antri/<%= bookId %>" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                  <svg width="14" height="14" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  Ya, Daftarkan Saya
                </button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item[data-page]').forEach(el => {
    if (el.dataset.page === 'antrian') el.classList.add('active');
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
